<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Student Resume</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .resume {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px gray;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: darkblue;
        }

        hr {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="resume">

    <h1>Student Resume</h1>

    <h2>Personal Information</h2>
    <p><b>Name:</b> John Doe</p>
    <p><b>Email:</b> johndoe@example.com</p>
    <p><b>Phone:</b> +91 9876543210</p>
    <p><b>Address:</b> Mumbai, India</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Career Objective</h2>
    <p>
        To obtain a challenging position in a reputed organization where I can utilize my skills
        and contribute to organizational growth.
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Education</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>B.Sc. Computer Science - XYZ University (2023 - 2026)</li>
        <li>HSC - ABC Junior College (2021 - 2023)</li>
        <li>SSC - PQR School (2021)</li>
    </ul>

    <hr>

    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>HTML, CSS, JavaScript</li>
        <li>PHP & MySQL</li>
        <li>Bootstrap Framework</li>
        <li>Basic Python Programming</li>
    </ul>

    <hr>

    <h2>Hobbies</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Reading Books</li>
        <li>Coding</li>
        <li>Playing Cricket</li>
    </ul>

    <hr>

    <h2>Declaration</h2>
    <p>
        I hereby declare that the above information is true to the best of my knowledge.
    </p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
